00:21:23.723 --> 00:21:25.523
15, 14.

352
00:21:25.523 --> 00:21:26.523
Dia sudah melempar bolanya!

353
00:21:26.523 --> 00:21:27.723
13!

354
00:21:27.723 --> 00:21:28.723
Di sini!

355
00:21:31.223 --> 00:21:33.323
Strike tiga!

356
00:21:37.523 --> 00:21:39.423
Jangan jawab itu! Berikan padaku!

357
00:21:42.223 --> 00:21:43.923
Halo? Halo?

358
00:21:45.323 --> 00:21:49.223
Hei, kau! Apa yang lucu?

359
00:21:49.223 --> 00:21:50.623
Sangat menarik.

360
00:21:50.623 --> 00:21:53.723
Kalian jelas menarik.

